-- Mellanox Surges to Record High, Closes Gap With U.S. Shares
-- B y   S h o s h a n n a   S o l o m o n
-- 2012-06-19T07:43:05Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-06-19/mellanox-surges-to-record-high-closes-gap-with-u-s-shares.html
 Mellanox Technologies Ltd., an
Israeli developer of technology used to transfer and store data,
rose to a record high, closing the gap with the U.S.-traded
shares.  The  shares  gained 4.8 percent to 276.30 shekels, or the
equivalent of $71.56, at 10:16 a.m. in  Tel Aviv , the highest
level since they were listed in Israel in July 2007. The New
York-traded stock advanced 7.2 percent to $71.53 yesterday.  To contact the reporter on this story:
